[
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">revealed</st> the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">word</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span><n id=\"1\" /> to <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<p class=\"paragraphtitle\">The Ark of the Covenant is Lost to the Philistines<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelites</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">went out</st> to <st data-num=\"07122 04421\">fight</st> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> They <st data-num=\"02583\" class=\"\">camped</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"072\" class=\"\">Ebenezer</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> and the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"02583\" class=\"\">camped</st> at <st data-num=\"0663\" class=\"\">Aphek</st>. ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"06186\" class=\"\">arranged</st> their forces to <st data-num=\"07122\" class=\"\">fight</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. As the <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">spread out</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> was <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">defeated</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">by</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>, who<n id=\"4\" /> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">killed</st> about <st data-num=\"0702 0505\" class=\"\">4,000</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> in the <st data-num=\"04634\" class=\"\">battle line</st> in the <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">field</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came back</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04264\" class=\"\">camp</st>, the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> did the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> let us be <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">defeated</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">by</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>? Let\u2019s <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">take</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st> us the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> from <st data-num=\"07887\" class=\"\">Shiloh</st>. When it <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"07130\" class=\"\">with</st> us, it will <st data-num=\"03467\" class=\"\">save</st> us<n id=\"3\" /> from the <st data-num=\"03709\" class=\"\">hand</st> of our <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> to <st data-num=\"07887\" class=\"\">Shiloh</st>, and they <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">took</st> from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sits</st> between the <st data-num=\"03742\" class=\"\">cherubim</st>. Now the <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st>, <st data-num=\"02652\" class=\"\">Hophni</st> and <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st>, were <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">When</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"04264\" class=\"\">camp</st>, <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"07321\" class=\"\">shouted</st> <st data-num=\"08643 01419\">so loudly</st><n id=\"1\" /> that the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">ground</st> <st data-num=\"01949\" class=\"\">shook</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of the <st data-num=\"08643\" class=\"\">shout</st>, they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> is <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">loud</st> <st data-num=\"06963 08643\">shout</st> in the <st data-num=\"04264\" class=\"\">camp</st> of the <st data-num=\"05680\" class=\"\">Hebrews</st>?\u201d Then they <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">realized</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">at</st> the <st data-num=\"04264\" class=\"\">camp</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">were scared</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">thought</st> that <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st> had <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04264\" class=\"\">camp</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> They <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">Woe</st> to us! We\u2019ve <st data-num=\"03588 03808 0865 08032\">never</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">seen</st> anything like <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>!",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0188\" class=\"\">Woe</st> to us! <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> can <st data-num=\"05337\" class=\"\">deliver</st> us from the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"0117\" class=\"\">mighty</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st>? <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">These</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">are</st> the <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">gods</st> who <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">struck</st> the <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egyptians</st> with <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all sorts of</st> <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">plagues</st> in the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">desert</st>! ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">Be strong</st> and <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">act</st> like <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st>, you <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>, <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">or else</st> you will wind up <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serving</st> the <st data-num=\"05680\" class=\"\">Hebrews</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">the way</st> they have <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">served</st> you! <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Act</st> like <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> and <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">fight</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">fought</st>. <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> was <st data-num=\"05062\" class=\"\">defeated</st>; they <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">ran</st> <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">home</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">slaughter</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> <st data-num=\"03966\" class=\"\">very</st> <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great;</st> <st data-num=\"07970 0505\" class=\"\">30,000</st> <st data-num=\"07273\" class=\"\">foot soldiers</st> from <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"05307\">fell in battle</st>. ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> was <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken</st>, and the <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st>, <st data-num=\"02652\" class=\"\">Hophni</st> and <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st>, were <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">killed</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">On <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"0376 01144\">Benjaminite</st> <st data-num=\"07323\" class=\"\">ran</st> from the <st data-num=\"04634\" class=\"\">battle lines</st> and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> to <st data-num=\"07887\" class=\"\">Shiloh</st>. His <st data-num=\"04055\" class=\"\">clothes</st> were <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">torn</st>, and <st data-num=\"0127\" class=\"\">dirt</st> was <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> his <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>. ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "When he <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> in Shiloh, <st data-num=\"02009 05941\">Eli</st> was <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sitting</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">in</st> his <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">chair</st> <st data-num=\"06822\" class=\"\">on the lookout</st><n id=\"1\" /> by the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">side</st> of<n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">road</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">he</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st> very <st data-num=\"02730\" class=\"\">worried</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">about</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. As the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">entered</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> to <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">give</st> his <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">report</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st> <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cried out</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> the <st data-num=\"06963 06818\">outcry</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"01995\" class=\"\">commotion</st>?\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> The <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"04116\" class=\"\">quickly</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> and <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">told</st> <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st>. ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "Now <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st> was <st data-num=\"08673\" class=\"\">ninety</st>-<st data-num=\"08083\" class=\"\">eight</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">old</st> and his <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">looked straight ahead</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> he was <st data-num=\"03808 03201\">unable</st> to <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"05941\" class=\"\">Eli</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> am the one who <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"04634\" class=\"\">battle lines</st>! Just <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">today</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">fled</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">from</st> the <st data-num=\"04634\" class=\"\">battle lines</st>!\u201d Eli<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">asked</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">How</st> did <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">things</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">go</st>, my <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>?\u201d ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">messenger</st> <st data-num=\"06030 0559\">replied</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> has <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">fled</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">from</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st>! The <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> has <st data-num=\"01571 01961\">suffered</st> a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"04046\" class=\"\">defeat</st>! Your <st data-num=\"08147\" class=\"\">two</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st>, <st data-num=\"02652\" class=\"\">Hophni</st> and <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st>, <st data-num=\"01571 04191\">are dead</st>! The <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> has been <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">captured</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"01961\">When</st> he <st data-num=\"02142\" class=\"\">mentioned</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>, Eli<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fell</st> <st data-num=\"0322\" class=\"\">backward</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> his <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">chair</st> <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">beside</st> the <st data-num=\"08179\" class=\"\">gate</st>. He <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">broke</st> his <st data-num=\"04665\" class=\"\">neck</st> and <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">died</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">he</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"02204\" class=\"\">was old</st> and <st data-num=\"03515\" class=\"\">heavy</st>. <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">He</st> had <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">judged</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> for <st data-num=\"0705\" class=\"\">40</st> <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">His <st data-num=\"03618\" class=\"\">daughter-in-law</st>, the <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">wife</st> of <st data-num=\"06372\" class=\"\">Phinehas</st>, was <st data-num=\"02030\" class=\"\">pregnant</st> and close to <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">giving birth</st>. When she <st data-num=\"08085 08052\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">that</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> was <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">captured</st> and that her <st data-num=\"02524\" class=\"\">father-in-law</st> and her <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">husband</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">were dead</st>, she <st data-num=\"03766\" class=\"\">doubled over</st> and <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">gave birth</st>. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> her <st data-num=\"06735\" class=\"\">labor pains</st> <st data-num=\"02015\">were too much</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">for</st> her.",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">As</st> she was <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">dying</st>, the women who <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">were there</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">with</st> her <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>! You have <st data-num=\"03588 03205\">given birth to</st> a <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>!\u201d But she did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06030\" class=\"\">reply</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"07896\" class=\"\">pay</st> any <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">attention</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">She <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">named</st> the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">boy</st> <st data-num=\"0350\" class=\"\">Ichabod</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u201cThe <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">glory</st> has <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">departed</st> from <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,\u201d referring <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">capture</st> of the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">and</st> the deaths of her <st data-num=\"02524\" class=\"\">father-in-law</st> and her <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">husband</st>. ",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "4",
    "text": "She <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cThe <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">glory</st> has <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">departed</st> from <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> the <st data-num=\"0727\" class=\"\">ark</st> of <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> has been <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">captured</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  }
]